00:17:38.789 --> 00:17:42.470
Most European nations have banned it and we're
the only ones left. So I think we need to

00:17:42.470 --> 00:17:44.960
abolish that law.

00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:48.789
But the-the last thing, really the heart of
the book and why it's called Dear Dr. Thompson,

00:17:48.789 --> 00:17:55.859
is that I think all of us should write our
own letters. Write a letter that changes somebody's

00:17:55.859 --> 00:18:02.899
life. Develop a software, write a book, write
a memo, do something that changes our world.

00:18:02.899 --> 00:18:08.629
